Package: pkgsite
Title: Minimal Static HTML Documentation for R Packages
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Mauricio", "Vargas Sepulveda", , "m.vargas.sepulveda@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1017-7574"))
Description: Generate minimal static HTML documentation websites from R packages. 
    Creates simple sites with basic navigation, function reference, and articles 
    using lightweight templates without complex theming or Bootstrap dependencies.
